      "message": "Is there a reason for this guard? It seems to break compilation on Linux \u0026 macOS in our environment, where we build with -fno-exceptions.\n\nEven with -fno-exceptions, the noexcept specialization above doesn\u0027t match other uses applied to functions without the noexcept specifier.",
